      <div class="membershipFaq" id="membershipFaq1">
        <h3 class="membershipFaq__question" id="membershipFaq__question1">Can I combine discounts?</h3>
        <p class="membershipFaq__answer" id="membershipFaq__answer1">You cannot combine additional discounts or promotions
          with your SISU VIP, but you will always get 20% off all in-store items while an active member regardless of how many
          purchases you make.</p>
      </div>
